{
  "id": "adv_bond_yu_01_04",
  "title": "鈴村優4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "お風呂あがったわ。優、次どうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm done with my bath. Yu‚ you're next",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.6000000715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "はーい…………くんくんくんくん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okaaaay…… Sniff‚ sniff‚ sniff‚ sniff",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3666667382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "な、何？　なんか変な匂いでも……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what? Do I smell weird or something…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.2000000715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、なんやめっちゃええ匂いするなぁ～\nこれってもしかして、うちがあげたやつ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ wow‚ you smell really good~\nIs this by any chance the one I gave you…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1000000715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。この前、優がくれたシャンプーを使ってみたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I tried the shampoo you gave me the other day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4999993085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "めっちゃ嬉しいわぁ～！　いい香りやし、髪がさらさら\nになるから、瑠依ちゃんにも使ってほしかってん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so happy! The scent is great and it makes your hair\nso silky‚ so I really wanted you to use it‚ Rui-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4999993085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "今までいろんなシャンプーを使ってきたけど\n香りも、使い心地も、一番好きかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've tried many shampoos before‚ but\nI might like this one's scent and feel the best of all",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8666659752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんに気に入ってもらえて良かったわぁ\nすみれちゃんにもプレゼントしたんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so glad you liked it‚ Rui-chan\nI gave one to Sumire-chan‚ too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3999977826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルみんなで同じシャンプー使ったら\nトークのネタになりそうちゃう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If all of TRINITYAiLE use the same shampoo‚\ndon't you think it could be a good topic for our talks?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6999977826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "確かに。何気ない日常も、話題に出来るのは強いわね\nラジオのトークとかも困らなくなりそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True. Being able to turn everyday life into a topic is a strength\nIt'll probably help with radio talks‚ too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.1666659752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "そうやねん。日々、ネタを探さな\nあかんなーって思ってたんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly. I've been thinking that I need to\nlook for new material every day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4666659752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "他にも、歯磨き粉やタオルとか、みんなで\nお揃いがええなーって思うねんけど、どうやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides that‚ for things like toothpaste and towels‚\nI think it'd be nice if we all matched. What do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.0333326418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "そこまでするの……？\nまぁ、お仕事のためになるのならいいけれど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You'd go that far…?\nWell‚ if it helps with our work‚ I don't mind",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.8000003258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、それじゃあ\n明日からお揃い期間スタートしよなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ well then\nlet's start our \"matching period\" tomorrow!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1333336591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "（瑠依ちゃんとお揃いの歯磨き粉使って）\n（シャンプーもタオルも一緒のブランドで……あっ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Using the same toothpaste as Rui-chan）\n（The same brand of shampoo and towels… Wait!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7666669924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "（使うもの全部お揃いにしたら、うちが瑠依ちゃんに）\n（瑠依ちゃんがうちになったも同然やん！！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If we match everything we use‚ then I'm Rui-chan）\n（and Rui-chan has basically become me!!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1999942223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "（あかん、うち、めっちゃ天才かもしれん！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh man‚ I might be a total genius!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7666634321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "優……？　考え込んでどうしたの？\nお風呂冷めちゃうわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu…? What are you thinking about so deeply?\nThe bath water is going to get cold",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.0333280642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_04-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "んー？　なんでもないで\nほな、お風呂行ってきます～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm? It's nothing~\nWell‚ I'm off to the bath now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.6999947309,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}